      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="37482988">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/bruchris/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u44312180-11.jpg" alt="懒人胡渣渣" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37482988/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37482988/" class="">十八</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/bruchris/" class=" " title="懒人胡渣渣">懒人胡渣渣</a>
                (空気読めない人)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="37482988">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">这样的教育是学校与社会完全无关，学生毕业以后可干什么去？只有两条出路：做官与当教员。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-03-30 20:58</span>
                  
                </p>
